M|Exam|- AR|$100/month
M|Exam|- Cu|1,000
M|Exam|- MR|$100K
M|Exam|- Ch|3%/month
M|Exam|- Ne|50
M|Exam|**Pr|**
M|Exam|- Ne|$120/month (+20%)
M|Exam|- Ex|Grandfathered at $100
M|Exam|**Im|**
M|Exam|- Ne|$120 (+20%)
M|Exam|- Ch|lo (existing protected)
M|Exam|- Co|Minimal (<5% drop estimated)
M|Exam|**Re|** im. Net rv impact +$12K/year w/ lo risk.
M|Exam|tx|---
M|Exam|**Sc|** 30% price increase for all cs
M|Exam|**Cu|**
M|Exam|- AR|$50/month
M|Exam|- Cu|5,000
M|Exam|- MR|$250K
M|Exam|- Ch|5%/month (already hi)
M|Exam|**Pr|**
M|Exam|- Al|$65/month (+30%)
M|Exam|**Im|**
M|Exam|- AR|+30% = +$75K MRR
M|Exam|- Ch|hi (5% → 8% estimated)
M|Exam|- Ch|3% × 5,000 × $65 = -$9.75K MRR/month
M|Exam|**Ne|** +$75K - $9.75K = +$65K MRR (but accelerating churn problem)
M|Exam|**Re|** Don't change. Fix retention first (reduce 5% churn), then raise prices.
M|Exam|tx|---
